snippet.textDisplay: So if it was created by an individual and not any documented facility, how would we ever know? It's not impossible to create this independently, and if that be, you can be sure there would be no regulations on its containment, and perhaps intention to not contain it too. In any case, most likely an accident and who ever is responsible probably doesn't even know they are.
